00:00:48.639 --> 00:00:50.639
It's going to run it.

00:00:50.639 --> 00:00:52.639
And it's going to say,

00:00:52.959 --> 00:00:54.959
And then it's going to think about it.

00:00:54.959 --> 00:00:56.959
Ask the tool.

00:00:56.959 --> 00:00:58.959
It's going to respond.

00:00:58.959 --> 00:01:00.959
