and finish them. Some things I want

00:13:50.479 --> 00:13:52.479
to add in is to have

00:13:52.479 --> 00:13:54.479
cleaner error detection in reporting.

00:13:54.479 --> 00:13:56.479
OpenTelemetry does a nice job

00:13:56.479 --> 00:13:58.479
to say, here's an error, here's the error message,

00:13:58.479 --> 00:14:00.479
possibly even

00:14:00.479 --> 00:14:02.479
